---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us | CryptoBonusList" description="Who runs CryptoBonusList and why it exists. No corporate fluff.">
  <section class="px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">
        ABOUT <span class="text-[#39FF14]">US</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-8 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#39FF14] mb-10">
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          CryptoBonusList started because we got tired of reading the same recycled bonus reviews on every affiliate site. Copy-paste descriptions, inflated ratings, zero useful information.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We built something different. Every bonus on this site is reviewed by people who have deposited, played through the wagering, and dealt with the withdrawal process firsthand.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 border-b-[3px] border-[#39FF14] pb-2">
        WHAT WE DO
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We review crypto casino bonuses. Welcome packages, no-deposit offers, reload deals, rakeback programs. If a casino runs a bonus for crypto depositors, we look at it.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          The focus is on the numbers. Wagering requirements, max bet limits, game contributions, withdrawal caps. The stuff that determines whether a bonus is worth taking or not.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We also cover crypto gambling news. Regulation changes, network fee updates, new coin support at casinos. Anything that affects how you deposit, play, and withdraw.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 border-b-[3px] border-[#39FF14] pb-2">
        HOW WE MAKE MONEY
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          Affiliate links. When you click through to a casino from our site and sign up, we get a commission. That is the business model. No subscriptions, no premium content, no paywalls.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          This does not change how we review bonuses. A bad bonus with a high commission is still a bad bonus. We would rather send you somewhere useful and keep you coming back.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 border-b-[3px] border-[#39FF14] pb-2">
        THE TEAM
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          Small team. Everyone plays at crypto casinos. Some of us have been in the space since the early days of Bitcoin gambling. Others joined when the Ethereum casino wave picked up.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We do not publish bylines or staff bios. The content speaks for itself. If a review is accurate and useful, it does not matter who wrote it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 border-b-[3px] border-[#39FF14] pb-2">
        WHAT WE DO NOT DO
      </h2>
      <div class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-6 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#FAFF00]">
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans]">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#FAFF00] font-bold mt-0.5">X</span>
            <span>Rate casinos on a 1-10 scale with no explanation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#FAFF00] font-bold mt-0.5">X</span>
            <span>Publish reviews for casinos we have not tested</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#FAFF00] font-bold mt-0.5">X</span>
            <span>Push bonuses that are mathematically bad for the player</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#FAFF00] font-bold mt-0.5">X</span>
            <span>Guarantee winnings or promise results</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#FAFF00] font-bold mt-0.5">X</span>
            <span>Accept payment to change a review</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          Questions or feedback? Reach out through the <a href="/contact" class="text-[#39FF14] underline underline-offset-4 decoration-2">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
